measurements.description: Six flowers of good form and dark color and four buds on two upright 40-cm inflorescences; dorsal sepal white, overlaid chartreuse centrally, heavily overlaid maroon proximally, veined maroon; petals chartreuse, blotched mahogany proximally, consistently rolled, spathulate, purple distally; synsepal chartreuse, veined darker; pouch chartreuse, overlaid mahogany, veined darker, staminode chartreuse, mottled darker green; substance firm; texture matte, pouch texture glossy.
